      "type": "n_trusted-reviews",
      "blocks": {
        "slider_AbTEJa": {
          "type": "slider",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/ellie_6_treatments.webp",
            "flag": "shopify://shop_images/america_f.webp",
            "username": "Ellie V.",
            "verified_customer": "Verified customer",
            "text": "<h6>My skin returned to life!</h6><p>“I just turned 57 years. My skin was extremely dry and while using this product my skin RETURNED to LIFE! I am so impressed with it! My coworkers ask me what I use in my skin.. and I tell them. Product easy to use... This is an amazing product that you will not regret in purchasing it. I really see the change in my skin. Outstanding job QURE!”</p>"
          }
        },
        "slider_qPwgBB": {
          "type": "slider",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Image_5_b0173f3a-3914-4db7-94ba-236f4cf89e4b.png",
            "flag": "shopify://shop_images/uk_flag.svg",
            "username": "Helen M.",
            "verified_customer": "Verified customer",
            "text": "<h6>I’m so impressed</h6><p>“I purchased the mixed Micro-Infusion bundle to deal with hyper pigmentation, fine lines and wrinkles. I also have rosacea so was worried it could make it worse. However I’m so impressed with the initial results 3 treatments in. My skin looks clear and fresh! Previously the redness and pigmentation was visible even through foundation. I have more confidence now and hope my skin continues to improve with further treatments.”</p>"
          }
        },
        "slider_6GYBm3": {
          "type": "slider",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Image_32_082e297a-5044-49ab-9ff8-f592a9352d7b.png",
            "flag": "shopify://shop_images/uk_flag.svg",
            "username": "Alix F.",
            "verified_customer": "Verified customer",
            "text": "<h6>Fantastic!</h6><p>“I am thoroughly enjoying using this product. I am on treatment 2 of 6 and already the difference in my skin is astounding. It’s smoother, tighter, plumper and looks so much healthier. My spots, pigmentation and redness are all so much calmer.  I will absolutely repurchase and am so glad I gave it a go!”</p>"
          }
        },
        "slider_xqgHn6": {
          "type": "slider",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/jessica-k.webp",
            "flag": "shopify://shop_images/america_f.webp",
            "username": "Jessica K.",
            "verified_customer": "Verified customer",
            "text": "<h6>Thrilled with the results!</h6><p>“I have been using the mask & microneedling for 6 weeks & am truly impressed with the results. I have noticed a dramatic reduction in redness, an improvement in the look of my dark spots, scars & overall skin tone & feel of firmness, and a smoothing of the look of fine lines & wrinkles.”</p>"
          }
        },
        "slider_78E6pj": {
          "type": "slider",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/andrea.webp",
            "flag": "shopify://shop_images/america_f.webp",
            "username": "Andrea G.",
            "verified_customer": "Verified customer",
            "text": "<h6>Definitely be re-ordering</h6><p>“Still a newbie but so far so great! I have dermarolled for more than a decade-still do with .25 at least one a week. I’ve avoided getting a pen because there’s so much involved-but the Qure system is just awesome. So easy and user friendly and my skin loves the serum! Doing my third treatment Saturday and will definitely be re-ordering 🤗</p>"
          }
        },
        "slider_eCGH8c": {
          "type": "slider",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/mona-p.webp",
            "flag": "shopify://shop_images/america_f.webp",
            "username": "Mona P.",
            "verified_customer": "Verified customer",
            "text": "<h6>Fade after just two treatments</h6><p>“I personally think my products absorbed better, my skin looks a bit brighter and that larger acne scar on my right cheek has started to fade after just TWO treatments!”</p>"
          }
        },
        "slider_JwXnch": {
          "type": "slider",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Image_2_9c05b808-aa78-4254-8031-9fea7eda6afe.png",
            "flag": "shopify://shop_images/usa_flag.svg",
            "username": "Janeda T.",
            "verified_customer": "Verified customer",
            "text": "<h6>What an amazing product this is.</h6><p>“I’ve done two treatments so far since I got this and my gosh, I have an extreme loss of dark spots. My skin is smooth and I got the dark spot treatment, but it Oohh amazed at this I keep telling everybody about this I cannot believe what an amazing product this is I will continue to buy it, and I will not stop using this for a treatment that you would spend $300 in the salon for just one treatment, how amazing is it to be able to do it at home?”</p>"
          }
        },
        "slider_MHwxjr": {
          "type": "slider",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Image_18_84ad7aed-73d2-49a7-a97c-88e4e0c2932c.png",
            "flag": "shopify://shop_images/america-flag_f1f6c160-90c6-4ba9-8bfc-d9039a28d2af.webp",
            "username": "Matias T.",
            "verified_customer": "Verified customer",
            "text": "<h6>Love it!</h6><p>“I’m 46 years old and have struggled with breakouts my whole life. Sadly, it wasn’t until I turned 40 that I started really taking care of my mature skin, the sagging, and wrinkles. This product, along with my skincare routine for mature skin, has made such an incredible difference—I’m absolutely thrilled! I can’t recommend it enough!!!”</p>"
